---- MODULE WindowLifecyclePlusCal ----
\* Gossamer webview window lifecycle from creation to destruction. Controls show/hide/run/destroy transitions.
\* PlusCal version — generated by tlaiser
\* https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

CONSTANTS Uninitialized, Hidden, Visible, Running, Closed

